title: 5 Easy Steps to be More Self Disciplined
itunes:title: 5 Easy Steps to be More Self Disciplined
description:
Discipline has a bad connotation but SELF-discipline is what you need to create the life you want. In this episode, I am going to teach you 5 steps to be more disciplined so that you can get more done!
